# Pagination — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/pagination.css`

## CSS Classes

### Base
- `.acko-pagination` — flex, items-center, gap-1, flex-wrap

### Page Button
- `.acko-pagination-btn` — `var(--scale-40) × var(--scale-40)`, `border-radius: var(--radius-full)` (circle shape), flex center, cursor-pointer
- Font: `--font-body-sm-size`, weight 500, family inherit
- Background: transparent
- Transition: `all 200ms var(--ease-in-out-cubic)` — smooth background/color changes

### Nav Buttons (Prev/Next)
- `.acko-pagination-nav` — `var(--scale-40) × var(--scale-40)`, `border-radius: var(--radius-full)`
- Background: `--color-surface-raised`
- Transition: `all 200ms var(--ease-in-out-cubic)`

### Ellipsis
- `.acko-pagination-ellipsis` — `var(--scale-40) × var(--scale-40)`, centered, `--color-text-muted`

### Info
- `.acko-pagination-info` — `--font-body-sm-size`, `--color-text-muted`

### Page Button States

| State | Background | Text | Extra |
|-------|-----------|------|-------|
| Default | transparent | `--color-text-default` | — |
| Hover | `--color-primary-subtle` | `--color-text-strong` | — |
| Current (`.acko-pagination-btn-current`) | `--color-primary-subtle` | `--color-text-default` | font-weight 600 |
| Disabled | transparent | `--color-text-muted` | `opacity: var(--opacity-48)`, `cursor: not-allowed` |

### Load More
- `.acko-pagination-load-more` — `border-radius: var(--radius-full)`, bg `--color-primary`, text `--color-on-primary`

## Display Pattern
`< 1 2 3 4 ...16 >` — handled by `getVisiblePageRange` in React component
